{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a7e5bb1262","title":"对钟赤兵关于民航机构设置和领导关系的建议的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7146af704a","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":11,"articleId":"a7e5bb1262"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"211ade147f","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a7e5bb1262","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"钟赤兵，当时任人民革命军事委员会民用航空局局长。"},{"id":"b8b94879ea","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a7e5bb1262","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指钟赤兵1952年3月10日关于民航局工作问题给毛泽东并中央的报告中提出的建议。这些建议是：（一）将民航现行机构分立为民航局和民航公司。前者为行政管理机关，尽量紧缩精简；后者为经营业务机构，按经济核算制来执行业务，在业务上财务上是独立的企业单位。（二）将民航局拨归空军建制，以利统一领导。（三）现有人员和干部由空军统一调整，不适合的转业建设，多余飞机交空军，工厂设备交重工业部，以达到通盘筹划和充分利用之效。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bf2c20f6d2","type":"title","text":"对钟赤兵以关于民航机构设置和领导关系的建议的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a7e5bb1262"},{"id":"211ade147f","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a7e5bb1262"},{"id":"b8b94879ea","type":"paragraph","text":"钟赤兵对民航局的建议值得注意。现在民航事业行政和业务混杂，领导多头，飞机和工厂浪费，他提议予以改变。请召集一会议予以研究，决定适当解决办法","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a7e5bb1262"},{"id":"f371247be4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a7e5bb1262"},{"id":"ffdcef56b4","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a7e5bb1262"}],"page":{"id":"7de5978c1c","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a7e5bb1262","start":500,"end":500}}}},"__N_SSG":true}